    <p>To create a thumbnail, you must save a low-quality version of a picture with smaller dimensions. Then, you should link this low-quality picture to its 
    higher-quality counterpart.</p>
    <ul class="list-group">
      <li class="list-group-item">
        <strong>THUMBNAIL Example:</strong>
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        <pre><code><?php $t->cHTML('<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
     <head>
         <title> 
            <!-- Title Here -->
         </title>
         <!--Code Here-->
     </head>
     <body>
        <a href="images/yourphoto.jpg"><img src="thumb_yourphoto.jpg" /></a>
     </body>
</html>
'); ?>
</code></pre>
      </li>
    </ul>
